text: Tomáš Prokop (born January 30, 1994) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for Hokej Šumperk 2003 of the Czech 1.liga. Prokop made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with Motor České Budějovice during the 2012-13 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Motor České Budějovice players Category:Stadion Hradec Králové players Category:Hokej Šumperk 2003 players Category:Czech ice hockey defencemen
